@page "/checklist"

<PageTitle>Checklist</PageTitle>

<main>
    <section class="page-hero">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="eyebrow">Documentation</div>
        <h1>Word File Coverage <span class="gradient-text">Checklist</span></h1>
        <p>This checklist compares the current HTML website against the original content brief and marks each section as covered, partial, or missing.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <div class="container panel">
        <span class="mini-label">Summary</span>
        <p><span class="status-badge status-covered">Covered</span> means the requested content exists in the site. <span class="status-badge status-partial">Partial</span> means it exists but still needs real values, assets, or backend wiring. <span class="status-badge status-missing">Missing</span> means it has not been added yet.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <div class="container">
        <table class="checklist-table">
          <thead>
            <tr>
              <th>Section</th>
              <th>Requirement</th>
              <th>Status</th>
              <th>Notes</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            <tr>
              <td>A. Brand Identity</td>
              <td>
                <ul>
                  <li>Website: www.kohinoorea.com</li>
                  <li>Tagline</li>
                  <li>Brand colors</li>
                </ul>
              </td>
              <td><span class="status-badge status-covered">Covered</span></td>
              <td>Domain, tagline, and color direction are used across the site.</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>A. Brand Identity</td>
              <td>Logo: Working</td>
              <td><span class="status-badge status-partial">Partial</span></td>
              <td>A text-based K mark is used now. The final brand logo file has not been added yet.</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>B. Home Page</td>
              <td>Strong headline, benefits, CTA buttons</td>
              <td><span class="status-badge status-covered">Covered</span></td>
              <td>Implemented on the home page with headline, benefit cards, and CTAs.</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>B. Home Page</td>
              <td>Limited offer banner text</td>
              <td><span class="status-badge status-covered">Covered</span></td>
              <td>Shown in the home hero banner.</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>C. About EA</td>
              <td>EA intro, how it works, strategy type, why choose it, problem solved, manual vs automated</td>
              <td><span class="status-badge status-covered">Covered</span></td>
              <td>All requested About EA sections are present on the About page.</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>C. About EA</td>
              <td>Limited offer text and CTA area</td>
              <td><span class="status-badge status-covered">Covered</span></td>
              <td>Included as a promo panel near the bottom of the About page.</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>D. Features Page</td>
              <td>Fully automated, risk management, MT4, high accuracy, easy setup, XAUUSD support</td>
              <td><span class="status-badge status-covered">Covered</span></td>
              <td>All feature topics are listed on the Features page.</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>E. Performance Page</td>
              <td>Myfxbook / live results, backtest report, growth chart</td>
              <td><span class="status-badge status-partial">Partial</span></td>
              <td>Sections and embed slots are ready, but real live-result URLs or report assets are still missing.</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>F. Pricing Page</td>
              <td>Monthly, annual, lifetime plans, annual highlighted, launch promo code</td>
              <td><span class="status-badge status-partial">Partial</span></td>
              <td>Plan structure, highlight state, and promo code are present. Exact numeric prices and savings were not provided.</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>F. Pricing Page</td>
              <td>Free trial / demo to registration page</td>
              <td><span class="status-badge status-covered">Covered</span></td>
              <td>The pricing page links to the registration page for trial or demo flow.</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>F. FAQ Page</td>
              <td>Main FAQ list from the brief</td>
              <td><span class="status-badge status-covered">Covered</span></td>
              <td>The FAQ page includes the requested questions and answers.</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>G. Common Questions</td>
              <td>All brokers, minimum deposit, refund policy</td>
              <td><span class="status-badge status-partial">Partial</span></td>
              <td>Broker and refund policy content is present. Minimum deposit is still generic because no exact value was provided.</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>H. Contact Page</td>
              <td>WhatsApp, Telegram, email</td>
              <td><span class="status-badge status-covered">Covered</span></td>
              <td>All three contact methods are wired with live links.</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>H. Contact Page</td>
              <td>Contact form ready</td>
              <td><span class="status-badge status-partial">Partial</span></td>
              <td>The form exists, but it currently uses a mailto fallback instead of a proper backend form service.</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>Sales Flow</td>
              <td>Plan-specific CTA buttons, WhatsApp order links, support links</td>
              <td><span class="status-badge status-covered">Covered</span></td>
              <td>Pricing and contact pages include plan-specific conversion paths.</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>Publishing Readiness</td>
              <td>Final logo, exact prices, final minimum deposit, live result assets, form backend</td>
              <td><span class="status-badge status-missing">Missing</span></td>
              <td>These are the remaining items needed to move from draft marketing site to fully finalized production content.</td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <footer class="site-footer">
    <div class="container footer-grid">
      <div><strong>Kohinoor EA</strong></div>
      <div><p>Checklist generated from the original brief for coverage review.</p></div>
    </div>
  </footer>


